<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Gym Reviews</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-image: url('/images/reviewbg.jpg');
            background-position: center;
            background-size: cover;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        #navbar{
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .home-button {
           
            color: white;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 18px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: white;
        }
        .review-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            border: 2px black;
            box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
            gap: 20px;
        }
        .review-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 15px;
            width: 250px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 2px black;
            box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
        }
        .stars {
            color: gold;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="navbar">
    <h1>PureCare Reviews</h1>
    <a href="/" class="home-button">Home</a>
    </div>
    <div class="review-container">

        <div class="review-card">
            <h3>Prabhas</h3>
            <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
            <p>This gym has everything I need! The equipment is top-notch and the staff is incredibly helpful. I love the variety of classes offered!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="review-card">
            <h3>Siddharth</h3>
            <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
            <p>Great atmosphere! The trainers are very knowledgeable, but I wish the locker rooms were a bit cleaner.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="review-card">
            <h3>Johnson</h3>
            <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
            <p>I’ve seen amazing results since joining! The personal training options are fantastic, and the community vibe keeps me motivated.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="review-card">
            <h3>Rajesh Kapoor</h3>
            <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐</div>
            <p>It's a decent gym overall, but I think it could use more cardio machines during peak hours. The staff is friendly, though!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="review-card">
            <h3>Aishwaraya Roy</h3>
            <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
            <p>Absolutely love this gym! The classes are varied and fun, and the instructors really push you to do your best!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="review-card">
            <h3>Rithu varma</h3>
            <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐</div>
            <p>Not a bad gym, but I found the membership fees to be a bit high compared to others in the area. The equipment is good, though!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="review-card">
            <h3>Revanth Reddy</h3>
            <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
            <p>This place is great for both beginners and seasoned athletes. The group classes are energizing!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="review-card">
            <h3>Shake Jani Basha</h3>
            <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
            <p>The gym is always clean, and I appreciate the 24-hour access. Perfect for my busy schedule!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="review-card">
            <h3>Mohammadh Ismail</h3>
            <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐</div>
            <p>Good selection of equipment, but it can get crowded during peak hours. Still a solid gym!</p>
        </div>
        <div class="review-card">
            <h3>Sai Reddy</h3>
            <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
            <p>Love the community feel! The staff is always encouraging, making workouts fun and effective.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="review-card">
            <h3>Jagadeesh</h3>
            <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
            <p>Overall a solid experience! I do wish they had more variety in their weightlifting equipment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="review-card">
            <h3>Soundharya</h3>
            <div class="stars">⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐</div>
            <p>The best gym I've ever joined! The trainers really care about your progress, and the classes are awesome!</p>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>